{
  "stem": "2966.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one ghetto was closed up, which we called liquidated, and we were all went into the second part of town, to one ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a very small amount of people left already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe there was 2,000, 3,000 people left, not even then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that time, we still kept on working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My sister was hidden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister was hidden in a place-- we had a power station [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that the Russians, when they were running away in 1941, they blew it up, so there was no electricity in town.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that power station evidently had some underground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was never there and never seen it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was quite a few people, maybe 50, 60 people hidden there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my sister was one of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German knew-- the Germans knew about it, but they couldn't find the entrance to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so it was only my father and me in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But one night-- we knew-- we knew that it's not going to last forever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we used to have guards-- our people, myself, all the young people-- we used to sit on the perimeter of the ghetto at night for a few hours, changing guards, to see whether the Germans are surrounding the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And truthfully one night, they did surround the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father and myself were taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were taken away with a few hundred, maybe 500, 600 people-- other people-- to a gathering place which was behind the headquarters of the Ukrainian police.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We're sitting there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Germans were all around those with dogs, with those vicious dogs.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
